BOEING AIRCRAFT COMPANY v. TRANSCONTINENTAL & WESTERN AIR, Inc. No. 9333. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 9, 1939. Todd, Holman & Sprague, of Seattle, Wash., for appellant. Eggerman & Rosling, of Seattle, Wash., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, DENMAN, and STEPHENS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed, that a judgment of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and that the mandate of this court in this cause issue forthwith.
